{"type":"message","id":"89c01aa7","parentId":"67521c86","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:48:23.197Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Mission Control issues — three problems to fix:\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n1. AGENT SPRITES MISSING ON DASHBOARD\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nOn the Dashboard (/) and Agent Office (/visual), agent sprites \nshow as empty square boxes — no pixel art visible. Status symbols \nand text appear correctly. The sprite images ARE loading on the \nTeams page, so the image files exist and work in some places but \nnot others.\n\nCheck:\n- What's different about how the Dashboard/AgentOffice loads sprites \n  vs the Teams page?\n- Are the sprite file paths correct? Compare the src attributes \n  between Teams (working) and Dashboard (broken)\n- Check browser Console for any 404 or image load errors on / and \n  /visual\n- Check the build output — are sprite PNGs in the client assets?\n  We had a Vite Cloudflare build issue before where sprite PNGs \n  weren't copied to the client build\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n2. SCHEDULER PAGE NOT LOADING\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nThe Scheduler page (/scheduler) is not loading at all. It was \npreviously working after the rename from calendar.tsx → scheduler.tsx.\n\nCheck:\n- curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | head -20\n- Any build errors related to scheduler?\n- Did the route registration break during the cleanup rounds?\n- Check the browser Console for errors when navigating to /scheduler\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n3. ROOT CAUSE + FIX\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nFix both issues. Report what caused each one. Commit when resolved.\n\nVerify:\n- curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -o \"sprite\\|\\.png\" | head -10\n- curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | wc -c (should be > 1000)\n- All routes return 200: /, /visual, /scheduler, /tasks, /team","timestamp":1780058902509,"idempotencyKey":"e987c8bc-dba0-4bfe-b971-d3079889d66c:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0e359bc","parentId":"89c01aa7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:48:43.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nI'll fix all three issues. Let me start by investigating in parallel."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"6c80ca4a-575d-4d0c-83b4-5ab0416bf046","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"Investigate sprite issue — compare Dashboard vs Teams sprite loading","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"Investigate Scheduler page routing issue","status":"pending"},{"step":"Fix both issues","status":"pending"},{"step":"Verify all routes return 200","status":"pending"},{"step":"Commit and push","status":"pending"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"plan\": [{\"step\": \"Investigate sprite issue — compare Dashboard vs Teams sprite loading\", \"status\": \"in_progress\"}, {\"step\": \"Investigate Scheduler page routing issue\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Fix both issues\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Verify all routes return 200\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Commit and push\", \"status\": \"pending\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":17918,"output":119,"cacheRead":4736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":22773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780058903200,"responseId":"gen-1780058903-TDqE2vZmDtk0v7wWLcu5"}}
