{"type":"message","id":"73f47872","parentId":"ddc19c09","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:52:47.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK, the URLs DO resolve in dev mode. So the sprite images actually load! The user said sprites show as \"empty square boxes.\" This could mean the images load but the `<img>` tag has no content (0×0) because of CSS — maybe `object-contain` on a container without explicit dimensions.\n\nLet me re-read the user's report: \"Status symbols and text appear correctly. The sprite images ARE loading on the Teams page.\" So it's a rendering issue, not a loading issue. Let me look at how the Dashboard/Spacestation renders sprites vs how Team does it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ac8f8c68-fbba-4d2f-bc48-ea7a8645e8cb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && cat src/routes/team.tsx | head -80","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && cat src/routes/team.tsx | head -80\", \"timeout\": 5}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"74a01c45-26e8-4690-8161-6e9a2c56bc79","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep -n \"w-20\\|h-20\\|w-14\\|h-14\\|w-7\\|h-7\\|max-w\\|max-h\\|Width\\|Height\\|width\\|height\" src/components/Spacestation.tsx | head -20","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep -n \\\"w-20\\\\|h-20\\\\|w-14\\\\|h-14\\\\|w-7\\\\|h-7\\\\|max-w\\\\|max-h\\\\|Width\\\\|Height\\\\|width\\\\|height\\\" src/components/Spacestation.tsx | head -20\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":375,"output":260,"cacheRead":60800,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":61435,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780059137459,"responseId":"gen-1780059137-OzW20dovcxwOOpVCOMzM"}