{"type":"message","id":"0cf41482","parentId":"39c495b0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:13:20.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"9648cf7e-aa62-4b46-9f19-58bd9251b924","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git add src/components/AgentOffice.tsx src/routes/scheduler.tsx src/components/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx src/components/scheduler/useCronData.ts && git rm -r src/routes/scheduler/ && git commit -m \"fix: agent sprites missing on Dashboard + Scheduler page not loading\n\nIssue 1 - Agent Sprites:\n- SPRITES map was populated inside useEffect() which doesn't run during SSR\n- Server rendered <img> tags with no src attribute (empty string)\n- Fix: moved CREW.forEach SPRITES initialization outside useEffect to module scope\n- All 4 agent sprites now render with correct image paths on Dashboard/AgentOffice\n\nIssue 2 - Scheduler page:\n- src/routes/scheduler/ directory conflicted with src/routes/scheduler.tsx\n- TanStack Router scanned CronJobCard.tsx and useCronData.ts as route files\n- Caused route ID collision ('schedulerscheduler') and hydration failure\n- Fix: moved helper files to src/components/scheduler/ (non-route directory)\n- Scheduler page now renders correctly with full content\"","timeout":15},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git add src/components/AgentOffice.tsx src/routes/scheduler.tsx src/components/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx src/components/scheduler/useCronData.ts && git rm -r src/routes/scheduler/ && git commit -m \\\"fix: agent sprites missing on Dashboard + Scheduler page not loading\\n\\nIssue 1 - Agent Sprites:\\n- SPRITES map was populated inside useEffect() which doesn't run during SSR\\n- Server rendered <img> tags with no src attribute (empty string)\\n- Fix: moved CREW.forEach SPRITES initialization outside useEffect to module scope\\n- All 4 agent sprites now render with correct image paths on Dashboard/AgentOffice\\n\\nIssue 2 - Scheduler page:\\n- src/routes/scheduler/ directory conflicted with src/routes/scheduler.tsx\\n- TanStack Router scanned CronJobCard.tsx and useCronData.ts as route files\\n- Caused route ID collision ('schedulerscheduler') and hydration failure\\n- Fix: moved helper files to src/components/scheduler/ (non-route directory)\\n- Scheduler page now renders correctly with full content\\\"\", \"timeout\": 15}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":219,"output":260,"cacheRead":153856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":154335,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780060364730,"responseId":"gen-1780060364-XRA2QDVaL0iEL4ZTHdHi"}}
{"type":"message","id":"244b1602","parentId":"0cf41482","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:13:20.602Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"9648cf7e-aa62-4b46-9f19-58bd9251b924","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"rm 'src/routes/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx'\nrm 'src/routes/scheduler/useCronData.ts'\n[main 18bfb94] fix: agent sprites missing on Dashboard + Scheduler page not loading\n 4 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)\n rename src/{routes => components}/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx (100%)\n rename src/{routes => components}/scheduler/useCronData.ts (100%)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":58,"aggregated":"rm 'src/routes/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx'\nrm 'src/routes/scheduler/useCronData.ts'\n[main 18bfb94] fix: agent sprites missing on Dashboard + Scheduler page not loading\n 4 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)\n rename src/{routes => components}/scheduler/CronJobCard.tsx (100%)\n rename src/{routes => components}/scheduler/useCronData.ts (100%)","cwd":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780060400602}}
