{"type":"message","id":"0298ca0a","parentId":"4d62874c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:09:27.642Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Good work on the sprite and scheduler fixes. Two new issues introduced:\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n1. ROOM BACKGROUNDS MISSING\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nAgent sprites now visible, but the room backgrounds (Command HQ, \nSecurity Bay, Engineering, Archive) are not showing. The room images \nthat were previously rendering are now gone. Check:\n- Did the AgentOffice.tsx change affect room background loading?\n- Are the room image imports still intact?\n- Compare with the Teams page where images DO work\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n2. GREY BOX AROUND SPRITES — REMOVE IT\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nEach agent sprite has a grey box/background behind it. This should \nbe removed — only the pixel art sprite should show, no border, no \nbackground box. The sprite PNGs have transparent backgrounds. Check:\n- Is there a wrapper div with background/border styling on the \n  sprite elements?\n- Is there a CSS class adding bg-card or similar?\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n3. SCHEDULER — SPINNING WHEEL\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nYou said the scheduler is fixed but I'm still seeing a spinning \nloading wheel. The page doesn't fully render. Check:\n- curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | wc -c\n- Is there a client-side hydration error in the browser Console?\n- Did the route fix fully deploy? Check the dev server is running \n  the latest build\n\n═══════════════════════════════\nVerify all three fixes. Commit when done.","timestamp":1780063766874,"idempotencyKey":"43ce1ec7-3866-4c57-95d4-222afd441ec7:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae5862e3","parentId":"0298ca0a","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:10:11.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLet me investigate all three issues in parallel."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"14c0a85e-f458-4db3-9e18-9bf04fa8cbb9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -o '<img[^>]*>' | head -20","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -o '<img[^>]*>' | head -20\", \"timeout\": 10}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"3aac6ae0-07e1-45a2-960f-308607fd6493","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | wc -c && echo \"---\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | strings | grep -o '\"s\":\"success\"' | head -5 && echo \"---\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | strings | grep \"lucide-loader\\|animate-spin\" | head -5","timeout":15},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | wc -c && echo \\\"---\\\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | strings | grep -o '\\\"s\\\":\\\"success\\\"' | head -5 && echo \\\"---\\\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | strings | grep \\\"lucide-loader\\\\|animate-spin\\\" | head -5\", \"timeout\": 15}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"64e1e0b4-ce91-4958-873c-3e81eefae9cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -o 'room.*png\\|room-.*v2' | head -10","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -o 'room.*png\\\\|room-.*v2' | head -10\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"inpu