{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\n\nAdditional context from HEARTBEAT.md:\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Task Pickup\n- Read `data/tasks.json`, find tasks with `status: \"backlog\"`\n- For each backlog task, spawn a sub-agent (or work directly if simple) to complete it\n- Move task to `in_progress` when starting, `done` when complete\n- Write completion summary before marking done (see task details)\n- Only pick up one task per heartbeat to avoid overloading\n- If a task is already `in_progress` and was started >2 hours ago with no progress update, reset it to backlog\n\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\n- If a sub-agent runs for >5 minutes with no resolution, kill it and add the task to backlog\n- If the main agent spends >10 minutes debugging the same issue, stop and add to backlog\n- Always report what was tried and what the blocker is when adding to backlog\nCurrent time: Friday, May 29th, 2026 - 3:12 PM (Europe/London)\nReference UTC: 2026-05-29 14:12 UTC","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"5f0411dd","parentId":"5da1900a","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:12:33.911Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"5e96ed4e","parentId":"5f0411dd","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:12:59.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm in the middle of fixing three issues for the user (room backgrounds, grey boxes around sprites, scheduler spinning wheel). Let me continue that work and also check heartbeat tasks."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ef6ad4f9-7f04-4263-a126-023608a5c81c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; tasks=json.load(sys.stdin); backlog=[t for t in tasks if t.get('status')=='backlog']; print(f'{len(backlog)} backlog tasks'); [print(f'  - {t.get(\\\"id\\\",\\\"?\\\")}: {t.get(\\\"title\\\",\\\"?\\\")}') for t in backlog[:5]]\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"No tasks.json or parse error\"","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \\\"import json,sys; tasks=json.load(sys.stdin); backlog=[t for t in tasks if t.get('status')=='backlog']; print(f'{len(backlog)} backlog tasks'); [print(f'  - {t.get(\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"?\\\\\\\")}: {t.get(\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"?\\\\\\\")}') for t in backlog[:5]]\\\" 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"No tasks.json or parse error\\\"\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":126334,"output":172,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":134314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780063953915,"responseId":"gen-1780063954-sooeUAiuymluKAS8ZqsK"}}
