{"type":"message","id":"3b38f19f","parentId":"6b485cea","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:29:07.162Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK, the SSR HTML contains the correct rendered content. The sprites now have src attributes, the rooms have canvas elements, and the scheduler renders fine on the server. The issues the user is seeing must be client-side hydration problems.\n\nLet me try to check if there's a hydration mismatch by looking at the actual client-side JS that gets loaded. Let me check if the `liveData` polling could be causing issues:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"68ef8359-d830-49a7-a16f-a9a830a8f00b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1,"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/AgentOffice.tsx"},"partialArgs":"{\"limit\": 30, \"offset\": 1, \"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/AgentOffice.tsx\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":219,"output":137,"cacheRead":158336,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":158692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780064907411,"responseId":"gen-1780064907-K1SVgk5n5bqWZbSTmQNi"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8d59989","parentId":"3b38f19f","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:29:07.199Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"68ef8359-d830-49a7-a16f-a9a830a8f00b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// src/components/AgentOffice.tsx\n// Main Agent Office orchestrator — the living, animated station view\n// Continuous floorplan, animated agents, status bubbles, walking movement\n\nimport { useEffect, useState, useCallback, useReducer, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"framer-motion\";\nimport { StationRoom } from \"./StationRoom\";\nimport { TaskFlowSignals } from \"./TaskFlowSignals\";\nimport { AmbientStation } from \"./AmbientStation\";\nimport { AgentTravel } from \"./AgentTravel\";\nimport { stationReducer, createInitialStationState, type StationState, type AgentActivity } from \"@/lib/station-state\";\nimport { useLiveStationData } from \"@/lib/live-data\";\nimport type { SystemStats } from \"@/lib/server-data\";\nimport { CREW } from \"@/lib/crew\";\nimport { getRandomChatter } from \"@/lib/delights\";\n\nconst ROOMS = [\n  {\n    id: \"command\",\n    label: \"COMMAND HQ\",\n    occupantId: \"monkey\",\n    accent: \"#6030c0\",\n    accentHue: 270,\n    agentPos: { xPct: 50, yPct: 65 },\n    monitors: [\n      { xPct: 15, yPct: 15, w: 20, h: 15, label: \"orbital\" },\n      { xPct: 40, yPct: 12, w: 22, h: 18, label: \"starmap\" },\n      { xPct: 68, yPct: 15, w: 18, h: 15, label: \"comms\" },\n    ],\n  },\n\n[313 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780064947199}}
{"type":"message","id":"48ac37d9","parentId":"c8d59989","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:29:49.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**There it is!** Line 6: `import { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"framer-motion\"` — this imports Framer Motion, which was supposed to be removed per the refactor history (commit `445ffa0 fix: replace Framer Motion with CSS-only animations`). \n\nThis is a **module-level import** of `framer-motion`. If Framer Motion is no longer installed or fails to load, this would cause a **module loading error**, which would prevent the entire client-side JS from executing. That would explain ALL three issues:\n1. Room backgrounds (canvas `useEffect` never runs)\n2. Grey boxes (JS error prevents proper rendering, fallback UI shows)\n3. Scheduler spinner (useCronData's `useEffect` fetch never fires)\n\nLet me check:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"56890eff-c939-43e1-a2fc-4c8c32f6400e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep \"framer-motion\" package.json","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep \\\"framer-motion\\\" package.json\", \"timeout\": 5}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"27b6f8c4-60a2-4271-9dc8-568e91c577d9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && ls node_modules/framer-motion/package.json 2>/dev/null && echo \"INSTALLED\" || echo \"NOT INSTALLED\"","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && ls node_modules/framer-motion/package.json 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"INSTALLED\\\" || echo \\\"NOT INSTALLED\\\"\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":638,"output":266,"cacheRead":158464,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":159368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse",