{"type":"message","id":"24898567","parentId":"58516075","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:00:55.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I can see the issues clearly now:\n\n1. **BUILD footer**: Shows `BUILD <!-- -->14fb84a` — the hash is there but there's a `<!-- -->` comment artifact between \"BUILD\" and the hash. The SSR is rendering `BUILD {BUILD_HASH}` but `BUILD_HASH` is being output as a separate text node.\n2. **bg-card/10**: Still showing 1 match — let me find where\n3. **Room backgrounds**: Canvas elements are present but empty (SSR can't draw on canvas)"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"dad44713-4144-4ec8-a174-db0f6fb55021","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -c 'bg-card/10'","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s http://localhost:3000/ | grep -c 'bg-card/10'\", \"timeout\": 10}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"64b719ed-2c64-47d0-bc62-230d3a4dffcc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"bg-card/10\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -n \\\"bg-card/10\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":16332,"output":207,"cacheRead":168192,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":184731,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780066787626,"responseId":"gen-1780066787-wnqaUBLMVYDBweQGRz8F"}}
