{"type":"message","id":"f1613e14","parentId":"c7365b54","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:03:43.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `scheduler` directory only has `CronJobCard.tsx` and `useCronData.ts` — no `index.tsx` or `scheduler.tsx` inside it. The route file is `src/routes/scheduler.tsx` (flat file). But there's also a `src/routes/scheduler/` directory!\n\n**This is the bug!** TanStack Router sees both:\n1. `src/routes/scheduler.tsx` → route `/scheduler` \n2. `src/routes/scheduler/` directory → it looks for `index.tsx` inside it but finds none, yet the directory itself might be interfering\n\nThe double `scheduler` in the route ID `schedulerscheduler` confirms this — TanStack is seeing both the file-based route and a directory-based route competing.\n\nActually wait — in TanStack Start, having `src/routes/scheduler.tsx` AND `src/routes/scheduler/` is a conflict. The file defines `/scheduler` and the directory would also try to define `/scheduler/` if it had an `index.tsx`. Without an `index.tsx` in the directory, the directory might be creating an empty/null route that interferes.\n\nThe fix: either rename the directory to `scheduler-page/` or move the route file. But the cleanest fix since the `scheduler/` directory holds `CronJobCard.tsx` and `useCronData.ts` (non-route files), is to prefix them with `-` to tell TanStack Router to ignore them as routes (per the error logs we saw earlier).\n\nLet me check the TanStack Router config:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"aabae3b9-40e5-4789-9f55-fee895f4bdad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep -rn \"routeFileIgnore\\|ignoreRoute\\|flatRoutes\\|scannedRoutes\" app.config.ts tsconfig.json . 2>/dev/null","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && grep -rn \\\"routeFileIgnore\\\\|ignoreRoute\\\\|flatRoutes\\\\|scannedRoutes\\\" app.config.ts tsconfig.json . 2>/dev/null\", \"timeout\": 5}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"90e6b996-336a-4225-a004-420cebe32ffd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && cat node_modules/@tanstack/react-start/dist/plugin/default-entry/routeTree.gen.ts 2>/dev/null | head -30 || find . -name \"routeTree.gen*\" -not -path \"*/node_modules/*\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && cat node_modules/@tanstack/react-start/dist/plugin/default-entry/routeTree.gen.ts 2>/dev/null | head -30 || find . -name \\\"routeTree.gen*\\\" -not -path \\\"*/node_modules/*\\\" 2>/dev/null\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":617,"output":480,"cacheRead":84736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":85833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780059485093,"responseId":"gen-1780059485-T0LoGTt0U7IobNrb7xtJ"}}
