{"type":"message","id":"dbefd259","parentId":"843a0b31","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:03:43.559Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Good work on the sprite and scheduler fixes. Two new issues introduced:\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n1. ROOM BACKGROUNDS MISSING\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nAgent sprites now visible, but the room backgrounds (Command HQ, \nSecurity Bay, Engineering, Archive) are not showing. The room images \nthat were previously rendering are now gone. Check:\n- Did the AgentOffice.tsx change affect room background loading?\n- Are the room image imports still intact?\n- Compare with the Teams page where images DO work\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n2. GREY BOX AROUND SPRITES — REMOVE IT\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nEach agent sprite has a grey box/background behind it. This should \nbe removed — only the pixel art sprite should show, no border, no \nbackground box. The sprite PNGs have transparent backgrounds. Check:\n- Is there a wrapper div with background/border styling on the \n  sprite elements?\n- Is there a CSS class adding bg-card or similar?\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n3. SCHEDULER — SPINNING WHEEL\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nYou said the scheduler is fixed but I'm still seeing a spinning \nloading wheel. The page doesn't fully render. Check:\n- curl -s http://localhost:3000/scheduler | wc -c\n- Is there a client-side hydration error in the browser Console?\n- Did the route fix fully deploy? Check the dev server is running \n  the latest build\n\n═══════════════════════════════\nVerify all three fixes. Commit when done.","timestamp":1780063766874,"idempotencyKey":"43ce1ec7-3866-4c57-95d4-222afd441ec7:user"}}
