{"type":"message","id":"23280e3c","parentId":"297baed0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:14:57.972Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That's the problem. The LaunchAgent restarted the server without the `VITE_BUILD_HASH` and `VITE_BUILD_TIME` env vars. Let me fix the `start-mc.sh` script to pass these properly, then restart via the LaunchAgent:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"82b0bb66-a153-424d-97ba-9c5b04b567eb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/scripts/start-mc.sh"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/scripts/start-mc.sh\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":238,"output":85,"cacheRead":27904,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":28227,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780067680948,"responseId":"gen-1780067681-bbiHLLqAaDMT2ujwQKhs"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d20d534c","parentId":"23280e3c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:14:58.018Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"82b0bb66-a153-424d-97ba-9c5b04b567eb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Start Mission Control dev server with build info injected via env vars\ncd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\"\n\nHASH=$(git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"dev\")\nTIME=$(date -u +\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ\")\n\necho \"[mc] Starting with build $HASH at $TIME\"\nexec env VITE_BUILD_HASH=\"$HASH\" VITE_BUILD_TIME=\"$TIME\" bun run dev --host --port 3000\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780067698018}}
{"type":"message","id":"d676ba4f","parentId":"d20d534c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:15:15.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The script looks correct. The issue is the LaunchAgent didn't run this script — it probably had a stale process or started without env vars. Let me check the LaunchAgent plist:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"64cd2e1c-f272-4c3f-9cdf-5d431cf0eaeb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/Library/LaunchAgents/com.spacemonkey.mission-control.plist"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/Library/LaunchAgents/com.spacemonkey.mission-control.plist\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":314,"output":71,"cacheRead":28032,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":28417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780067698023,"responseId":"gen-1780067698-J9ZtO4mte4zXybnfrmJs"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8182515","parentId":"d676ba4f","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:15:15.848Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"64cd2e1c-f272-4c3f-9cdf-5d431cf0eaeb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>com.spacemonkey.mission-control</string>\n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/bin/bash</string>\n        <string>/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/scripts/start-mc.sh</string>\n    </array>\n    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>\n    <string>/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard</string>\n    <key>RunAtLoad</key>\n    <true/>\n    <key>KeepAlive</key>\n    <true/>\n    <key>ThrottleInterval</key>\n    <integer>30</integer>\n    <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/logs/mission-control.log</string>\n    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/logs/mission-control-error.log</string>\n    <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>\n    <dict>\n        <key>PATH</key>\n        <string>/Users/spacemonkey/.bun/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin</string>\n    </dict>\n</dict>\n</plist>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780067715848}}
{"type":"message","id":"9704f2c8","parentId":"a8182515","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:15:40.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The plist looks correct — it runs `start-mc.sh` which sets env vars then exec's the server. The problem is `KeepAlive: true` means launchd will restart the process if it dies, but it restarts via the script (which is correct). Let me check the most recent log to see what happened:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"4292435e-d7c3-43c0-a169-5bcf01490846","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -30 ~/.openclaw/logs/mission-control.log 2>/dev/null","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"tail -30 ~/.openclaw/logs/mission-control.log 2>/dev/null\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":481,"output":107,"cacheRead":28288,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":28876,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780067715851,"responseId":"gen-1780067716-MA3qPgnQBIUlWOjjSliL"}}
