{"type":"message","id":"036951ff","parentId":"4652306b","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:44:16.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `export * from \"./helpers\"` is the problem. But the helpers functions (`readFileOrNull`, `readJsonOrNull`, `formatBytes`, `extractTitle`, `parseSize`) are used by the server modules. The pure JS ones (`formatBytes`, `extractTitle`, `parseSize`) don't use `node:fs` — only `readFileOrNull` and `readJsonOrNull` do.\n\nThe safest fix: **remove `export * from \"./helpers\"` from the barrel**. The server modules already import helpers directly via `\"./helpers\"`. Nothing else should import helpers from the barrel."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"c6011d0d-b6f9-4a08-adfe-1aaceae1df46","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/index.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"export * from \"./types\";\nexport * from \"./helpers\";","newText":"export * from \"./types\";\n// NOTE: Do NOT re-export helpers — it contains node:fs imports that leak into client bundle."}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/index.ts\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"export * from \\\"./types\\\";\\nexport * from \\\"./helpers\\\";\", \"newText\": \"export * from \\\"./types\\\";\\n// NOTE: Do NOT re-export helpers — it contains node:fs imports that leak into client bundle.\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":354,"output":229,"cacheRead":64768,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":65351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780083838363,"responseId":"gen-1780083838-M1Hol7vPTUw24iBiOXoD"}}
{"type":"message","id":"625b4261","parentId":"036951ff","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:44:16.640Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"c6011d0d-b6f9-4a08-adfe-1aaceae1df46","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/index.ts."}],"details":{"diff":"  1 // src/lib/server-data/index.ts — barrel export\n  2 \n  3 export * from \"./types\";\n- 4 export * from \"./helpers\";\n+ 4 // NOTE: Do NOT re-export helpers — it contains node:fs imports that leak into client bundle.\n  5 export * from \"./tasks\";\n  6 export * from \"./crons\";\n  7 export * from \"./memory\";\n  8 export * from \"./docs\";\n    ...","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/index.ts\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/index.ts\n@@ -1,8 +1,8 @@\n // src/lib/server-data/index.ts — barrel export\n \n export * from \"./types\";\n-export * from \"./helpers\";\n+// NOTE: Do NOT re-export helpers — it contains node:fs imports that leak into client bundle.\n export * from \"./tasks\";\n export * from \"./crons\";\n export * from \"./memory\";\n export * from \"./docs\";\n","firstChangedLine":4},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780083856640}}
{"type":"message","id":"27a3733c","parentId":"625b4261","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:44:28.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now fix `server-data.ts` which also re-exports helpers functions:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"bb72b867-f45c-486b-bab9-81b1e3531c20","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data.ts"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data.ts\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":371,"output":48,"cacheRead":65024,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":65443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780083856648,"responseId":"gen-1780083856-LAeu9DdSz73DAxvBoccg"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa3fd0b3","parentId":"27a3733c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:44:28.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"bb72b867-f45c-486b-bab9-81b1e3531c20","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// src/lib/server-data.ts — barrel export for all server data functions\n// Split into domain modules: server-data/{tasks,crons,memory,docs,projects,incidents,search,activity,system,agent-status,quick-actions,openclaw-status}.ts\n\nexport {\n  // Helpers\n  readFileOrNull, readJsonOrNull, formatBytes, extractTitle, parseSize,\n} from \"./server-data/helpers\";\n\n\nexport type {\n  // Types\n  Task, TaskHistoryEntry, QueueItem, CronJob, OpenClawCronJob,\n  SystemStats, AgentStatus, MemoryEntry, Doc, Project,\n  Incident, IncidentEvent, IncidentAction, CreateIncidentInput,\n  ActivityEvent, SearchResult, OpenClawStatus,\n  ActionResult, SystemHealth, AwaitingReviewResult, CronToggleResult,\n} from \"./server-data/types\";\nexport { WORKSPACE, OPENCLAW_DIR } from \"./server-data/types\";\n\nexport { getTasks, saveTasks, dispatchTask, getQueue } from \"./server-data/tasks\";\nexport { getCronJobs } from \"./server-data/crons\";\nexport { getDailyLogs, getLongTermMemory } from \"./server-data/memory\";\nexport { getDocs } from \"./server-data/docs\";\nexport { getProjects } from \"./server-data/projects\";\nexport { getIncidents, createIncident } from \"./server-data/incidents\";\nexport { search } from \"./server-data/search\";\nexport { getActivityFeed } from \"./server-data/activity\";\nexport { getSystemStats, getSystemHealth } from \"./server-data/system\";\nexport { getAgentStatus } from \"./server-data/agent-status\";\nexport {\n  restartGateway, clearCache, runFreerideRefresh, toggleDreaming,\n  pauseQueue, resumeQueue, restartMissionControl, runBackup,\n} from \"./server-data/quick-actions\";\nexport { getOpenClawStatus, getOpenClawCrons, getAwaitingReviewCount } from \"./server-data/openclaw-status\";\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780083868997}}
{"type":"message","id":"90a3564f","parentId":"fa3fd0b3","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:44:52.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This barrel also re-exports the fs-using helpers. And the **type** exports from `server-data/types` are also here — these are what components import. The problem: this file exports helpers (with node:fs) alongside types. When Vite sees `import type { SystemStats } from \"@/lib/server-data\"`, it may still resolve the whole module.\n\nThe fix: **create a separate types-only module** that components can import from without pulling in server code."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"f4d93a46-1bfe-4f0d-931c-d832352e7e23","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data-types.ts","content":"// src/lib/server-data-types.ts\n// Types-only re-export — safe for client components (no node:fs leak)\nexport type {\n  Task, TaskHistoryEntry, QueueItem, CronJob, OpenClawCronJob,\n  SystemStats, AgentStatus, MemoryEntry, Doc, Project,\n  Incident, IncidentEvent, IncidentAction, CreateIncidentInput,\n  ActivityEvent, SearchResult, OpenClawStatus,\n  ActionResult, SystemHealth, AwaitingReviewResult, CronToggleResult,\n} from \"./server-data/types\";\nexport { WORKSPACE, OPENCLAW_DIR } from \"./server-data/types\";\n"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data-types.ts\", \"content\": \"// src/lib/server-data-types.ts\\n// Types-only re-export — safe for client components (no node:fs leak)\\nexport type {\\n  Task, TaskHistoryEntry, QueueItem, CronJob, OpenClawCronJob,\\n  SystemStats, AgentStatus, MemoryEntry, Doc, Project,\\n  Incident, IncidentEvent, IncidentAction, CreateIncidentInput,\\n  ActivityEvent, SearchResult, OpenClawStatus,\\n  ActionResult, SystemHealth, AwaitingReviewResult, CronToggleResult,\\n} from \\\"./server-data/types\\\";\\nexport { WORKSPACE, OPENCLAW_DIR } from \\\"./server-data/types\\\";\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":580,"output":265,"cacheRead":65280,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":66125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780083869003,"responseId":"gen-1780083869-Tyuwb90TIZatrJLhztsN"}}
