{"type":"message","id":"deba2603","parentId":"58230ec6","timestamp":"2026-05-29T20:31:43.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. Let me trace each issue:\n\n**Issue 1: OpenClaw version shows 2026.5.12**\n- In `system.ts`, line: `openclawVersion: String(cfg?.version || \"unknown\")` — reads from `openclaw.json` → `cfg?.version`\n- The actual version is `2026.5.26` per `openclaw --version`. Let me check what `openclaw.json` actually has."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"4e9215fa-dd48-4119-a610-58ca2aacaa55","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"import json; cfg=json.load(open('/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/openclaw.json')); print('version:', cfg.get('version')); print('meta:', json.dumps(cfg.get('meta',{}), indent=2))\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"Failed to parse\"\necho \"=== Also check getSystemStats return ===\"\ngrep -n \"openclawVersion\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/system.ts","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"python3 -c \\\"import json; cfg=json.load(open('/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/openclaw.json')); print('version:', cfg.get('version')); print('meta:', json.dumps(cfg.get('meta',{}), indent=2))\\\" 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"Failed to parse\\\"\\necho \\\"=== Also check getSystemStats return ===\\\"\\ngrep -n \\\"openclawVersion\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/server-data/system.ts\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":3559,"output":234,"cacheRead":86016,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":89809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780086657355,"responseId":"gen-1780086657-egGBkSlehJZETP2oRQGp"}}
