{"type":"message","id":"7180ca09","parentId":"d9d1094b","timestamp":"2026-05-29T20:38:53.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"9f8a30a9-c385-48b3-8853-dd2d720e2497","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Gateway restart command ===\nGateway restart failed: Error: gateway port 18789 is still busy before LaunchAgent restart\nPort 18789 is already in use.\n- pid 70364 spacemonkey: /opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin/node /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789 (127.0.0.1:18789)\n- pid 70364 spacemonkey: /opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin/node /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789 ([::1]:18789)\nTip: openclaw gateway install\n\n=== Backup script exists? ===\n-rwx------  1 spacemonkey  staff  872 May 21 15:02 /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/openclaw-backup-quick.sh\n\n=== Quick dry-run of backup script head ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Quick Backup — Config only, runs fast\n# Backs up just the essential config and workspace files\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nSOURCE_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nBACKUP_BASE=\"/Volumes/Public/openclaw-agent-backup\"\nTIMESTAMP=$(date +\"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S\")\n\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick\" \"$BACKUP_BASE/logs\"\n\nBACKUP_FILE=\"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick/openclaw-quick_$TIMESTAMP.tar.gz\"\n\ntar -czf \"$BACKUP_FILE\" \\\n    -C \"$HOME\" \\\n    .openclaw/openclaw.json \\\n    .openclaw/agents/ \\\n    .openclaw/workspace/ \\\n    .openclaw/memory/ \\\n    .openclaw/identity/ \\\n    .openclaw/plugins/ \\\n    .openclaw/plugin-skills/ 2>/dev/null || true\n\necho \"Quick backup: $BACKUP_FILE ($(du -h \"$BACKUP_FILE\" | cut -f1))\"\n\n# Keep only last 5 quick backups\ncd \"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick\" && ls -t openclaw-quick_*.tar.gz 2>/dev/null | tail -n +6 | xargs rm -f 2>/dev/null || true"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1383,"aggregated":"=== Gateway restart command ===\nGateway restart failed: Error: gateway port 18789 is still busy before LaunchAgent restart\nPort 18789 is already in use.\n- pid 70364 spacemonkey: /opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin/node /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789 (127.0.0.1:18789)\n- pid 70364 spacemonkey: /opt/homebrew/opt/node/bin/node /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789 ([::1]:18789)\nTip: openclaw gateway install\n\n=== Backup script exists? ===\n-rwx------  1 spacemonkey  staff  872 May 21 15:02 /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/openclaw-backup-quick.sh\n\n=== Quick dry-run of backup script head ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Quick Backup — Config only, runs fast\n# Backs up just the essential config and workspace files\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nSOURCE_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nBACKUP_BASE=\"/Volumes/Public/openclaw-agent-backup\"\nTIMESTAMP=$(date +\"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S\")\n\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick\" \"$BACKUP_BASE/logs\"\n\nBACKUP_FILE=\"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick/openclaw-quick_$TIMESTAMP.tar.gz\"\n\ntar -czf \"$BACKUP_FILE\" \\\n    -C \"$HOME\" \\\n    .openclaw/openclaw.json \\\n    .openclaw/agents/ \\\n    .openclaw/workspace/ \\\n    .openclaw/memory/ \\\n    .openclaw/identity/ \\\n    .openclaw/plugins/ \\\n    .openclaw/plugin-skills/ 2>/dev/null || true\n\necho \"Quick backup: $BACKUP_FILE ($(du -h \"$BACKUP_FILE\" | cut -f1))\"\n\n# Keep only last 5 quick backups\ncd \"$BACKUP_BASE/backups/quick\" && ls -t openclaw-quick_*.tar.gz 2>/dev/null | tail -n +6 | xargs rm -f 2>/dev/null || true","cwd":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780087133582}}
